½In Loving Memory of
Ronald Willis
(Ron)
1937 - 2019
Please sit awhile and enjoy
this beautiful place,
where I used to fish as a boy
and in later years.
So to all those that think of me,
we will miss each other for a while
and if others wonder why I'm missin
just tell em' I've sens fishin"Ē
